R Notebook

資料來源:此資源來源於KAGGLE(https://www.kaggle.com/code/warathep11/video-games-sales-r)。

資料敘述:資料內容為1980-2018遊戲銷售內容(包含:PS4.XBOX.PC等),包含:遊戲名稱,遊戲平台,遊戲發行年,遊戲類型,遊戲出版商,以及遊戲銷售量(包含北美,歐洲,日本,其他,以及總銷售量)。

研究動機:欲了解遊戲的銷售情況受何種因素影響,例如:市場上銷量最好的遊戲比起其他遊戲的具有什麼不同,此因素可能是遊戲類型,發行年分等,而本研究目的之一便是了解各變數之於銷售的影響。

觀察遊戲銷售量隨著年增加

game_released <- vdo %>%
group_by(Year) %>%
summarize(number_of_games_released = n()) %>%
arrange(Year) %>%
mutate(cumsum_number_of_games_released=cumsum(number_of_games_released))

#Plot
options(repr.plot.width = 14, repr.plot.height = 8)
ggplot(game_released,aes(Year,cumsum_number_of_games_released)) +
geom_line(col='red') +
scale_x_continuous(breaks=c(1980:2016)) +
ylim(0,20000) +
theme(plot.title = element_text(hjust=0.5,size=16),
      axis.text.x = element_text(size=16,angle=45,vjust=0.5),
     axis.text.y = element_text(size=16),
     axis.title = element_text(size=16),
     legend.text=element_text(size=16),
     legend.title=element_text(size=16),
     plot.subtitle = element_text(hjust=0.5,size=14),
     panel.background = element_rect(fill = 'white', colour = 'grey50')) +
labs(x='Year',y='Number of Games Released',title='Number of Game Released Per Year',subtitle='Data from 1980 to 2016')

從上圖可以看出1980-1993遊戲銷量不高,而1994-2016遊戲銷售數量顯著增加

現在,檢視銷量最高的遊戲是哪些類型

#Data Manipulation 
vdo_sale <- vdo %>%
filter(Genre!='NA') %>%
group_by(Genre) %>%
summarize(North_America = sum(NA_Sales),
         Europe = sum(EU_Sales),
         Japan = sum(JP_Sales),
         Others = sum(Other_Sales)) %>%
pivot_longer(North_America:Others,
             names_to='Region',
            values_to='Sales')

#Plot
options(repr.plot.width = 14, repr.plot.height = 8)
ggplot(vdo_sale,aes(reorder(Genre,Sales),
                    Sales,fill=Region)) + 
geom_col(col='black') +
labs(x='Genre',y='Number of Sales (Millions)',title = 'Number of Sales for Each Genre Breakdown by Region',subtitle = 'Data from 1980 to 2016') +
theme(plot.title = element_text(hjust=0.5,size=16),
      axis.text.x = element_text(size=16),
     axis.text.y = element_text(size=16),
     axis.title = element_text(size=16),
     legend.text=element_text(size=16),
     legend.title=element_text(size=16),
     plot.subtitle = element_text(hjust=0.5,size=14)) +
coord_flip() +
geom_label(aes(label = stat(y),
              group = Genre), 
          stat = 'summary',
          fun = sum,
           hjust = -0.1,
           show.legend = FALSE
  ) +
ylim(0,2000)

1.大部分遊戲類型都以北美銷售量最多 2.日本在角色扮演遊戲的銷量中佔有更多的比例

資料預處理

sales_dataset1 = subset(vdo, select = -c(Name, Publisher, Developer))


# Exp 1 - train:test 70:30, seed 555

set.seed(567)
split = sample.split(sales_dataset1$Global, SplitRatio = 0.7)
train_dataset1 = subset(sales_dataset1, split == TRUE)
test_dataset1 = subset(sales_dataset1, split == FALSE)

資料切割為7:3 其中70%作為訓練資料 30%作為測試資料
